{
  "stem": "14060.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have seen people later on, when I was in the other work camp in Ramsdorf, who were perfectly healthy looking people-- I mean, perfectly healthy in the circumstances, as people looked at the time.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And once they started talking that we will never get out, we will get finished, this is the end, within a day or two, they were dead for no reason whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there is a lesson to be learned in normal life, not only in unreasonable circumstances, that the, the point of survival is to never give up hope.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because you don't know what's around the corner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Something-- just as well as a bad thing can happen-- something unusually good can happen as well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the people who gave up hope, they were finished and dead, gone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, there was another saying in the camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They said that all the good people didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Maybe they were too nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Maybe they didn't have the guts to, to, to, to-- you see, look, there were many.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Some were not healthy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, for instance, in Birkenau, they immediately, after the selection, a day or two after, they looked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If anybody had a hernia, they asked him to come out. you know, there were subsequent selections before the transport went away to a work camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyhow, within five days, we were put together, a transport of 6,000 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were commandeered down to the railway line into the cattle trucks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And off we went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We got a certain amount of ration.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember in early afternoon we left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we happily ate our rations up the same day, thinking that, you know, after all, something we would get.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
